Download pyinstaller
Run pyinstaller --onefile --windowed your_script_name.py
Rename your_script_name.exe screensaver.scr the .exe file should be in dist/
Move or Copy the .scr file to C:\Windows\System32\

Now press win + r and type control
Search the Change screen saver under Power Option
Choose from the drop list the new screen saver

That's all hope you enjoy :)